        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Fixed Asset Relief Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to increase the additional depreciation allowance (bonus depreciation) from 50% to 100% of the adjusted basis of qualifying business property and to make such increased allowance permanent. </p>]]></text>
